%% User Logout Sequence
%% Maps to: FR-4, FR-25

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client
    participant AuthController
    participant AuthService
    participant TokenService
    participant Transaction
    participant PostgreSQL
    participant Redis

    Client->>AuthController: POST /auth/v1/logout
    AuthController->>AuthController: Extract access token from Authorization header
    AuthController->>AuthController: Extract refresh token from httpOnly cookie

    AuthController->>AuthService: logout(accessToken, refreshToken)

    rect rgb(255, 245, 230)
        Note over Transaction,PostgreSQL: Transaction — Delete Refresh Token
        AuthService->>Transaction: createTransaction(async (tx) => { ... })
        Transaction->>PostgreSQL: BEGIN TRANSACTION
        Transaction->>TokenService: deleteRefreshToken(refreshToken)
        TokenService->>PostgreSQL: DELETE FROM auth_tokens WHERE token_hash = ? AND token_type = 'refresh'
        PostgreSQL-->>TokenService: Deleted
        Transaction->>Transaction: Auto-commit (no error)
        Transaction->>PostgreSQL: COMMIT
    end

    Note over AuthService,Redis: Blacklist access token (best-effort)
    AuthService->>TokenService: blacklistToken(accessToken)
    TokenService->>TokenService: Decode token to get access_token + expiry
    TokenService->>Redis: SET blacklist:{access_token} {expires_at, user_id}
    Note right of Redis: TTL = token expiry time
    Redis-->>TokenService: OK

    TokenService-->>AuthService: success
    AuthService-->>AuthController: success

    AuthController->>AuthController: Clear-Cookie (refreshToken)
    AuthController-->>Client: 200 OK + Clear-Cookie
